Olushola Odeyinde The Senate on Wednesday confirmed Mr. Lamido Yuguda as the Director-General of the Securities and Exchange Commission. The PUNCH reports. Reginald C. Karausa, Ibrahim D. Boyi, and Obi Joseph were also confirmed as full-time commissioners of the Commission. Ezrel Tabiowo, Special Assistant on Press to Senate President, Ahmed Lawan, announced in a statement that the nominees were confirmed after the Senate considered the report of the Committee on Capital Market. 